The '''Imperial University of Marngar III''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] school on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Marngar III]].

[[Thene Campus]] was part of the [[University/Legends|university]].

[[Benald Orlan]] attended the university before betraying his family to the Empire.

